{
  "stem": "26576.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I had friends, and I was going to have a profession.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I knew that by moving, I will lose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "But-- in-- in meantime, I started to go out with my husband more serious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And my husband had to run away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And already, he did not get a permission.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He had to run illegally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He had to smuggle already with a few friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I realized that whether I like it or not, I have to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So I've decided that I will go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And then my parents made some plans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And we left everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "My uncle came back from Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "One of my uncles that went to Russia came back from Russia, and he was a Communist, he stayed on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And he took over our flat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And we were-- we went-- we took both the ticket, and we went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And what did happen on the Czech border, in the middle of the night, again, KGB came, it wasn't KGB, it was UB, which was the Polish, Bezpieczenstwa, Polish KGB.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And they took off my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And they didn't say, you know-- they don't give any-- it's like Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They didn't tell you why [INAUDIBLE], they just took off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they said, you can go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But we decided that we won't go without him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was very traumatic, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I felt guilty that maybe if we would have gone earlier maybe that would not have happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "But finally, we went back, the whole family-- my mother, my sister, myself, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was in Paris already by that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a year in Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went 1947.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't have a house where to live, we stayed with some friends, which came later on to Australia.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
